provider_current Class

Usage

provider_current(
  title = character(0),
  description = character(0),
  contact = character(0),
  modified = character(0),
  identifier = character(0),
  download = character(0),
  issued = character(0),
  released = character(0),
  site = character(0)
)

Arguments

title

<chr> Endpoint title

description

<chr> Endpoint description

contact

<chr> Endpoint contact information

modified

<Date> Date Endpoint data was last modified

identifier

<chr> Endpoint url

download

<chr> Endpoint download url

issued

<Date> Date Endpoint data was issued

released

<Date> Date Endpoint data was released

site

<chr> Hyperlink to API landing page

Value

provider_current object
